    • Field Detail

      • ExpectedResponse

        public java.lang.String ExpectedResponse
        Name of head element of the response expected from the server for this request.

        E.g. :
        For a command request of
        <Operation><Command> <SessionID>1033</SessionID><SequenceNumber>2</SequenceNumber> <EventsCommand><Subscribe><All></All></Subscribe></EventsCommand> </Command></Operation>

        The head element name in the response would be CommandResponse as in
        <Operation><CommandResponse> <SequenceNumber>11</SequenceNumber><Result>0</Result> </CommandResponse></Operation>
